    TransformingList<I,O>

    public static class TransformingList.RandomAccess<I,O>
extends TransformingList<I,O>
implements java.util.RandomAccess
    A transforming list that supports random access to its elements. Any TransformingList that is wrapping a random access list supports efficient random access. But a standard TransformingList is missing the RandomAccess marker interface that is an important hint for many APIs (such as Collections.binarySearch(List, Object).
